title: Ochikobore Datta Ani ga Jitsu wa Saikyou: Shijou Saikyou no Yuusha wa Tenseishi, Gakuen de Mujikaku ni Musou suru
title_english: The Useless Brother Is Now the Strongest: The Mighty Brave Is Reincarnated and Nonchalantly Rules over the Academy
title_japanese: 落ちこぼれだった兄が実は最強 ～史上最強の勇者は転生し、学園で無自覚に無双する～
title_synonyms: My Older Brother Who Was a Dropout is Actually the Strongest
synopsis:
After a battle to the death with the Demon Lord, Brave Eugene is forcefully transported into the future of the world he had saved. Taking up his new role as "Julius," Eugene is met with disdain and contempt by his family and younger brother Gaias as the powerless loser of the school. However, having obtained the power and knowledge of his previous life, Julius now aims to show everyone what happens when the older brother gets serious!

(Source: Kodansha USA)
background: Ochikobore Datta Ani ga Jitsu wa Saikyou: Shijou Saikyou no Yuusha wa Tenseishi, Gakuen de Mujikaku ni Musou suru has been published digitally in English as The Useless Brother Is Now the Strongest: The Mighty Brave Is Reincarnated and Nonchalantly Rules over the Academy by Kodansha USA through K Manga.
